Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial
Condition.

On October 16, 2024, Morgan Stanley (the
"Company") released financial information with
respect to its quarter ended September 30,
2024. A copy of the press release containing
this information is annexed as Exhibit 99.1 to
this Report and by this reference incorporated
herein and made a part hereof. In addition, a
copy of the Company's Financial Data
Supplement for its quarter ended September 30,
2024 is annexed as Exhibit 99.2 to this Report
and by this reference incorporated herein and
made a part hereof.

The information furnished under Item 2.02 of
this Report, including Exhibit 99.1 and
Exhibit 99.2, shall be deemed to be "filed"
for purposes of the Securities Exchange Act of
1934, as amended.
